ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
SubjectCanada-British Columbia - Information Sharing ** Agreement **
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Citizenship and Immigration to enter into an INFORMATION SHARING AGREEMENT with BRITISH COLUMBIA for the purpose of facilitating the formulation, coordination and implementation including collection, use and disclosure of information - of policies and programs related to sponsorship, social assistance, refugee resettlement and asylum.
